{"tid":1641652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對準恐怖組織－守護香港大聯盟","createTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:14:23.000Z","uid":13289,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"68f17a691b3186362b1686a3580867d9dc10a9e4","tid":1641652,"uid":13289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"首先，同大家維基一下呢個守護香港大聯盟係咩黎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「守護香港大聯盟（英語：Safeguard HK, Support the Surrender of Fugitive Offenders Legislation），是由親建制派於2019年7月17日成立的支持修訂逃犯條例的組織。該聯盟以「保公義 護香港 撐修例」為口號，並在「護港安全修例大聯署」中收集簽名。其前身為4月16日成立的「萬眾同聲撐修例公義組」及5月10日「保公義撐修例大聯盟」[1]。」</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個所謂守護香港大聯盟，先莫講當初六月已經踢爆佢地做埋啲假聯署。之後更加多次舉辦撐警集會、撐警日，甚至同北角福建幫關系密切。而今日又聽到一個震撼消息，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">守護香港大聯盟將會捐款52萬元予長沙灣殺人的士司機，變相鼓勵更多藍絲司機殺人。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而作為呢個守護香港大聯盟嘅成員，相信都絕對唔止係藍，而係紅，紅到發黑。我從佢地官網名單一路睇（<a href=\"https://safeguardhongkong.hk/info/about-us）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsafeguardhongkong.hk%2Finfo%2Fabout-us%EF%BC%89&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=e5d585e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://safeguardhongkong.hk/info/about-us）</a> ，當中好多成員、所謂副召集人，都係一班建制派議員、律師。呢類人，最多幫佢地議員辦工室裝修，俾唔到咩壓力佢地。但係其他從商成員，例如頭幾位就見到嘅副召集人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">龍子明</span></strong>，一經google發掘，原來係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港宏利</span>保險高級行政區域總監</strong>，而我相信有唔少手足、淺黃、和理非都有用到宏利，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地係咪可以諗下點樣作出回應呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其他成員包括金利來集團主席、高鋒集團主席，我真係唔知香港人可以點樣對準，不過我相信我地仲有好多空間去對準呢班<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根正苗紅、出賣港人嘅渣滓</strong></span>（本人重申一向反對暴力）。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢班賺盡香港人錢，靠香港人起飛嘅商家，倒轉槍頭出賣港人，支持福建幫、支持殺人的士司機，如果今日唔俾壓力佢地，他日只會有更多福建幫、殺人的士司機嘅出現。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pk-11_T9hnS_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpk-11_T9hnS_1200x0.png&h=a0ab15c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a72d3baafabab2e48d2c2fca61e7e5b4b5a430b","tid":1641652,"uid":44906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG9aR7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG9aR7m.jpg&h=3ac45faa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定要推！"},{"pid":"b5e991fb92d958cc7c5111b957c691c3516bcabd","tid":1641652,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:05:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"86042b4c314ed09a858eaf7b462a1263fb816719","tid":1641652,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7069e805800a03ac33a9e04b39f0a6ec7f3a4d5b","tid":1641652,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:42:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有冇推去國際線?<br />\n依堆公司支持恐怖襲擊"},{"pid":"199c130664241880a4f8ecbc5d1ea9f99626809b","tid":1641652,"uid":255637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:44:04.000Z","msg":"呢個一定要列入裝修名單no.1"},{"pid":"0fbaefcc38d11dc723926094d298b571c6e54413","tid":1641652,"uid":204225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n要策劃恐怖襲擊既人付出代價<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87b60e464708875938d55fe05bfe94b39227d46","tid":1641652,"uid":13289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:22:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60a5e8b6bf92c673f754b515e766119dfa3dfc9a","tid":1641652,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"陳小春喺反黑話齋，要跟佢兵符，財神，親信<br />\n兵符福建佬而家當搞左<br />\n財神就係佢地"