犯條例草案<br />\nSources : <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/331626/逃犯條例-黃英豪-聯署撐修例者達40-7萬-稱政府一定微調方案\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F331626%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA-%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E6%92%90%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E8%80%85%E9%81%9440-7%E8%90%AC-%E7%A8%B1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%BE%AE%E8%AA%BF%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=aad2baec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/331626/逃犯條例-黃英豪-聯署撐修例者達40-7萬-稱政府一定微調方案</a><br />\n<br />\n7月份以守護香港大聯盟聯合召集人名義於金鐘添馬公園舉行的「守護香港」集會<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/781088/日報-港聞-黃英豪籲不蒙面不戴口罩-守護香港-集會團結反暴力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F781088%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=827f49a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fdaily%2Fhk%2F781088%2F%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E5%AE%88%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%8F%8D%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B&h=e7df21e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/daily/hk/781088/日報-港聞-黃英豪籲不蒙面不戴口罩-守護香港-集會團結反暴力</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8月份以守護香港大聯盟召集人名義發起8月10號「全民撐警日」<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473648-20190809.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473648-20190809.htm&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=e62c5ce0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473648-20190809.htm&h=913497e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473648-20190809.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n9月份於進出口界的業界專訪中提倡網絡安全法，限制網上發放信息<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190920/mobile/bkn-20190920173027057-0920_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190920%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190920173027057-0920_00822_001.html&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=fa876db5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190920/mobile/bkn-20190920173027057-0920_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n9月30 號於守護香港大聯盟活動上，向公眾指岀有人以 $2150 利誘未成年學生示威<br />\nSources : <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/黃英豪-有人以-2150-利誘未成年學生示威-對象是太太-閨蜜-外甥女/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5-2150-%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%98%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%AA-%E9%96%A8%E8%9C%9C-%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A5%E5%A5%B3%2F&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=03b9a0fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%BB%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%B1%AA-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%A5-2150-%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%98%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%AA-%E9%96%A8%E8%9C%9C-%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A5%E5%A5%B3%2F&h=967938ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/黃英豪-有人以-2150-利誘未成年學生示威-對象是太太-閨蜜-外甥女/</a><br />\n<br />\n10月9日以守護香港大聯盟名義向撞傷示威者的鄭姓司機募捐52萬元。<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1609051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1609051&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=9ee90da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1609051</a>"},{"pid":"acd03689ca21e38182ff54cec1d11bcfdb41ad0e","tid":1641652,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"堅係恐怖組織 開車撞人 元朗 荃灣 全部有份"},{"pid":"c06d4c3b84c7744803577029ea42b31a11b371f8","tid":1641652,"uid":245418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd03689ca21e38182ff54cec1d11bcfdb41ad0e","tid":1641652,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"堅係恐怖組織 開車撞人 元朗 荃灣 全部有份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"恐怖組織資金來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c45e3683ec31fa70f97c9ec9f9a58d7616f9cee","tid":1641652,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd03689ca21e38182ff54cec1d11bcfdb41ad0e","tid":1641652,"uid":247845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T07:39:37.000Z","msg":"堅係恐怖組織 開車撞人 元朗 荃灣 全部有份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"所以唔明點解美心太子女咁多人講<br />\n呢個恐怖組織成員無人理"},{"pid":"a9e2e40526ae2f3da30d9b8a472b74b7bce5f385","tid":1641652,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f17a691b3186362b1686a3580867d9dc10a9e4","tid":1641652,"uid":13289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:59.000Z","msg":"首先，同大家維基一下呢個守護香港大聯盟係咩黎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">「守護香港大聯盟（英語：Safeguard HK, Support the Surrender of Fugitive Offenders Legislation），是由親建制派於2019年7月17日成立的支持修訂逃犯條例的組織。該聯盟以「保公義 護香港 撐修例」為口號，並在「護港安全修例大聯署」中收集簽名。其前身為4月16日成立的「萬眾同聲撐修例公義組」及5月10日「保公義撐修例大聯盟」[1]。」</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個所謂守護香港大聯盟，先莫講當初六月已經踢爆佢地做埋啲假聯署。之後更加多次舉辦撐警集會、撐警日，甚至同北角福建幫關系密切。而今日又聽到一個震撼消息，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">守護香港大聯盟將會捐款52萬元予長沙灣殺人的士司機，變相鼓勵更多藍絲司機殺人。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而作為呢個守護香港大聯盟嘅成員，相信都絕對唔止係藍，而係紅，紅到發黑。我從佢地官網名單一路睇（<a href=\"https://safeguardhongkong.hk/info/about-us）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsafeguardhongkong.hk%2Finfo%2Fabout-us%EF%BC%89&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNicuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=e5d585e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://safeguardhongkong.hk/info/about-us）</a> ，當中好多成員、所謂副召集人，都係一班建制派議員、律師。呢類人，最多幫佢地議員辦工室裝修，俾唔到咩壓力佢地。但係其他從商成員，例如頭幾位就見到嘅副召集人<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">龍子明</span></strong>，一經google發掘，原來係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港宏利</span>保險高級行政區域總監</strong>，而我相信有唔少手足、淺黃、和理非都有用到宏利，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地係咪可以諗下點樣作出回應呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n其他成員包括金利來集團主席、高鋒集團主席，我真係唔知香港人可以點樣對準，不過我相信我地仲有好多空間去對準呢班<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>根正苗紅、出賣港人嘅渣滓</strong></span>（本人重申一向反對暴力）。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">呢班賺盡香港人錢，靠香港人起飛嘅商家，倒轉槍頭出賣港人，支持福建幫、支持殺人的士司機，如果今日唔俾壓力佢地，他日只會有更多福建幫、殺人的士司機嘅出現。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pk-11_T9hnS_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpk-11_T9hnS_1200x0.png&h=a0ab15c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"真，比錢個恐襲的士佬已經唔係政見問題，係支援恐怖份子"},{"pid":"a7ba625c5e6e6dd20f8baea3dc66621a1dbab1a9","tid":1641652,"uid":230942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T09:39:50.000Z","msg":"呢個19大聯盟支持恐怖主義<br />\n聯盟啲人是咪要制裁"},{"pid":"11f361872aa74a8bd77a5cdf958f360216fe8ae7","tid":1641652,"uid":13289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9682a4fddea5b6178ef18794b592f4192c0bea","tid":1641652,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2efcf1f34f61fb5ab68b092cd88b548a07ecaa20","tid":1641652,"uid":254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},{"pid":"46ec46e082b8ebe99ff9ca1d02fa26b790a2d586","tid":1641652,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"裝修佬standby"},{"pid":"125ac31d970bf2e9d081690abb05126d7038c5af","tid":1641652,"uid":47779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:13:06.000Z","msg":"龍子明有個仔以前讀香島 而家好似讀緊樹仁"},{"pid":"ba1e9ff07b2a654b310dc970f500ac9ae457219b","tid":1641652,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d6645bc32bf633f13c1ef6d285a9537bdf3caec","tid":1641652,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"推爆佢老母"},{"pid":"734b6898c0a405ed97f887053f6f46bf24c6bc33","tid":1641652,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"呢班真係牛鬼蛇神<br />\n<br />\n個肥仔黃英豪係咩料？"},{"pid":"00e972f43c16f52ecb53c86de66838a90f5d5b27","tid":1641652,"uid":88937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9f23737f1d7cc2bcf6fe28b1f6c0bed17f9f77b","tid":1641652,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078071f4668b44f283f01ab4a91b3fb66a74b594","tid":1641652,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"734b6898c0a405ed97f887053f6f46bf24c6bc33","tid":1641652,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"呢班真係牛鬼蛇神<br />\n<br />\n個肥仔黃英豪係咩料？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:35:18.000Z","msg":"除任香港黃乾亨黃英豪律師事務所的首席合伙人外，黃英豪還收購了兩家香港上市公司金至尊和海域化工（更名為香港資源）。<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki"},{"pid":"03140b88311900d2bf6192f4c7a4a05671a44e54","tid":1641652,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:17:01.000Z","msg":"唔止謝sir，連er er er sir都&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}